---
title: Cheesy Herby Chicken & Pearl Couscous Salad Bowl with Garlic Yoghurt & Lemon
description: Want a perfect meal for those sunny days? Look no further than this refreshing Mediterranean salad, packed full of tender chicken, fluffy pearl couscous and fresh, crunchy veggies, all drizzled with a creamy garlic yoghurt. It’s a vibrant meal that’ll leave you feeling satisfied and energised.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
